{"tid":1201983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請保持正確天氣及交通資訊流通 - 野餐篇","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:42:59.000Z","uid":3354,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2421bb52a9c89736ae4ccf76aed49733d78c6884","tid":1201983,"uid":3354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"睇住身邊唔同既朋友去野餐去露營 <br />\n但要返工請唔到假 或者各種因素無得去 真係好慘架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7YmrGtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7YmrGtM.png&h=1b25b0c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返緊工又無理由facetime架   咁不如同大家開返個天氣加交通消息既群組<br />\n扮下工傾下計都好吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議每個group 10-20個你真係識得 而又去野餐既朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(fd搭fd都儘量唔好喇 speed dating咩)<br />\n其中兩三個都係拎唔到假出唔到去既 隨時update最新天氣狀況同埋交通消息 <br />\n(有時行開行埋去個廁所 開個會都仲有人一齊吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n上網見到撞車呀停駛呀 或者有人轉發水浸都係黃雨 仲有圖既時候<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTJE1u5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTJE1u5.jpg&h=630ed841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先上網做齊fact check  先好轉發俾野餐中既朋友 <br />\n成為佢地最可以信賴既天氣先生/小姐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoH2Zg7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoH2Zg7.jpg&h=34456bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去緊野餐既都要send第一手交通資訊 (一定要係第一手 唔好亂轉發)俾扮工既朋友<br />\n例如邊到有人跌左出馬路 邊到有車死左火等等<br />\n然後扮工既一邊睇住直播新聞有無報導更多有關資訊<br />\n再負責提供其他轉乘既交通方法  <br />\n保持正確既交通消息互相流通 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCJtUQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCJtUQY.jpg&h=583be260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外 收到「我朋友係天文台做&hellip;」 「我親戚係交通警&hellip;」呢類既消息必須小心閱讀<br />\n呢d無需要負責任既轉發訊息睇過就算  野餐開開心心最唔需要就係呢d奇怪消息<br />\n收到既人停止轉發  每個人去行街睇戲食飯都會有危險既時候<br />\n互相照應小心就夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qWeg3OL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqWeg3OL.jpg&h=63e46d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n師奶既消息流通度咁強 更加要好好利用  <br />\n當家庭group出現長輩圖 改圖  舊圖 既時候<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMWSB7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMWSB7N.jpg&h=49004202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用你fact check左既資料 連埋source 叫一班師奶轉發返出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n fact check左唔好曬嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n戶外活動時 保持正確消息流通 你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739e2fd52dd609d5ebc1cb8f027167ccd38eae0","tid":1201983,"uid":3354,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:29:24.000Z","msg":"另外介紹一下最近都幾熱門既通訊工具： telegram<br />\n有唔同既bot可以加入群組 一齊玩遊戲鬥高分又得 用電話玩狼人都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨時可以改id名 同朋友一齊改返個兄弟名  閏蜜名幾開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有send相可以用send file既方法 唔會壓縮左圖檔<br />\n一班朋友 samsung iphone 華為都好 影完呃like大合照就唔怕變左低清圖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有常見又值得使用既天氣/交通消息發怖網站: <br />\nRTHK即時新聞  - <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/latest-news.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Flatest-news.htm&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b8b96942\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Flatest-news.htm&h=d299e956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/latest-news.htm</a><br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=4bce4a0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c</a> <br />\n全港即時最新交通消息<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/HK_Traffic_News\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_Traffic_News&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=9dd58adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_Traffic_News</a> <br />\nNOWTV新聞: <a href=\"https://now.com/home\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnow.com%2Fhome&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=d2c2ef13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://now.com/home</a><br />\nNOWTV 直播: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/live331a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive331a&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=036b7a15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flive331a&h=0bd34ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/live331a</a><br />\n有線即時新聞: <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/webapps/news_video/list_record.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fwebapps%2Fnews_video%2Flist_record.php&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=9c1fc504\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fwebapps%2Fnews_video%2Flist_record.php&h=7deebcc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/webapps/news_video/list_record.php</a><br />\n仲有立場新聞呀 獨媒等等 任君選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95cc83079609c14dd287eb251859c10